## What happens?

qiankun + mf + 普通webpack项目打包出的模块联邦使用起来会报错，主应用或者子应用单独使用时打包到生产环境都没有问题，报错信息如下
Uncaught (in promise) Error: Container initialization failed as it has already been initialized with a different share scope
    at Object.i (remoteEntry.js:2:1534620)
    at He (umi.js:578:1074)
    at async Promise.all (index 0)
    at async Promise.all (index 0)
    at async Promise.all (index 1)
![image](https://github.com/umijs/umi/assets/99160430/099d5778-4fcb-4921-a7c4-71eec05114ec)

## Mini Showcase Repository(REQUIRED)

可提供步骤如下

## How To Reproduce

**Steps to reproduce the behavior:** 1. 2.

**Expected behavior** 1. 2.

任意一个webpack库配置如下
```
const path = require('path');
const HtmlWebpackPlugin = require('html-webpack-plugin');
const { ModuleFederationPlugin } = require('webpack').container;
const deps = require('./package.json').dependencies;

const federationConfig = {
  name: 'opsc',
  filename: 'remoteEntry.js',
  exposes: {
    './XXX': './src/components/XXX',
  },
  shared: {
    react: { singleton: true, eager: true, requiredVersion: '18.2.0' },
    'react-dom': { singleton: true, eager: true, requiredVersion: '18.2.0' },
    antd: { singleton: true, eager: true, requiredVersion: '5.10.2'},
  }
};

module.exports = {
  resolve: {
    extensions: ['.js', '.jsx', '.ts', '.tsx'],
  },

  entry: './src/index.js',
  output: {
    publicPath: 'http://localhost:8001/remote/',
    filename: 'main.js',
    path: path.resolve(__dirname, 'dist'),
  },
  mode: 'production',
  module: {
    rules: [
      {
        test: /\.(js|mjs|jsx|ts|tsx)$/,
        include: path.resolve('./src'),
        loader: 'esbuild-loader',
        options: {
          loader: 'tsx',
        },
      },
    ],
  },
  plugins: [
    // ...
    new ModuleFederationPlugin({
      ...federationConfig,
    }),
    new HtmlWebpackPlugin({
      template: './src/index.html',
    }),
  ],
};
```
umi 主应用
```
{
...
  qiankun: { master: {} },
  mfsu: false,
  mf: {
    remotes: [
      {
        name: 'opsc',
        entry: 'http://localhost:8001/remote/remoteEntry.js',
      },
    ],
    shared: {
      react: { singleton: true, eager: true, requiredVersion: '18.2.0' },
      'react-dom': { singleton: true, eager: true, requiredVersion: '18.2.0' },
      antd: { singleton: true, eager: true, requiredVersion: '5.10.2' },
    },
  },
...
}
```
umi 子应用
```
  qiankun: {
    slave: {},
  },
  mfsu: false,
  mf: {
    remotes: [
      {
        name: 'opsc',
        entry: 'http://localhost:8001/remote/remoteEntry.js',
      },
    ],
    shared: {
      react: { singleton: true, eager: true, requiredVersion: '18.2.0' },
      'react-dom': { singleton: true, eager: true, requiredVersion: '18.2.0' },
      antd: { singleton: true, eager: true, requiredVersion: '5.10.2' },
    },
  },
```
按以上配置后，能够成功访问主应用并调用模块联邦，子应用也可以。但是主应用引入子应用时，就会出现图上报错
## Context

- **Umi Version**:     "@umijs/max": "^4.0.86",
- **Node Version**:  16
- **Platform**: linux

